</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-ARMAGEDDON (Undated) -- ``Armageddon'' is just another
cataclysm flick, although the cosmic cast is a bright spot. By Jay
Carr.
</P>
<P>
   MOVIE-BUFFALO (Undated) -- Although its limitations are
inescapably apparent, ``Buffalo 66'' is nevertheless an impressive
