little rich kid on ``Silver Spoons.'' But Ricky Schroder _ now
reinvented as Rick Schroder _ is all grown up, taking on a heavy
role as rookie detective filling in the shoes left by Jimmy Smits
on ``NYPD Blue.'' By Keith Marder. 
