<P>
   INTERVIEW-DAVID-CASSIDY (Bellevue, Wash.) David Cassidy, the
former teen heartthrob of ``The Partridge Family,'' is all grown up
and performing in (where else?) Las Vegas. He's also in Seattle
this week to promote a new album, on which he does covers of old
hits like ``I Think I Love You.'' We follow him to the Bellevue
Fred Meyer, where he will sign autographs. PHOTO
</P>
<P>
   By Teresa Talerico. (story will move in the ``e'' category)
