game against the Devil Rays in Tampa Bay. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Eds: First pitch is at 12:35 p.m. EDT
</P>
<P>
   BRAVES-STARS _ ATLANTA _ Braves lead all teams with six players
in the All-Star Game. Pitchers Greg Maddux and Tom Glavine and
reserves Javy Lopez and Andres Galarraga join starters Chipper
Jones and Walt Weiss. (Rosenberg, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
ETA: 8 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   LOPEZ _ KOHLER, Wis. _ If there's one thing Nancy Lopez wants to
do before she retires it's win the U.S. Women's Open. The Albany
resident has come close but never won. It's something she gears up
for every year. (Sheeley, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). ETA: 7
p.m.
