<HEADLINE>
`BURN RATE': INVESTING IN INTERNET AS CURE FOR OPTIMISM 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also moving in `e' category) 
(EDS: Publication notes appear at the end of the review.) 
(th) 
