 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    SURVIVAL OF THE FITTEST. Latin American banks are tightening
their belts to cushion future economic crises and compete against a
foreign onslaught.
 &HT;    Moved as BC-BANKING-BLUES-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``i''
international and ``f'' financial files.
