<HEADLINE>
BOSTON PEACE GROUP TO MONITOR IRISH MARCH 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By CINDY RODRIGUEZ  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON _ As thousands of Protestants &UR;  &LR; threaten to defy police
and march through a Catholic ghetto in Northern Ireland's Portadown
