<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BUSH-GINGRICH-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
(RESENDING TO FIX SLUG)  
BUSH, GINGRICH TARGET HISPANIC VOTE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MAX B. BAKER 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
