<HEADLINE>
COMPANY NEWS 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Mich, Texas, N.J., Del.)  (bl) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Champion Enterprises Inc., Auburn Hills, Mich., a maker of
prefabricated houses, said it had acquired ICA Group, which
operates 23 manufactured housing retail sites under the trade names
A-1 Homes, Homes of America and USA Homes.
</P>
<P>
   Metals USA Inc., Houston, bought two specialty metals processors
and two building-products distributors for an undisclosed price.
</P>
<P>
   Commerce Bancorp Inc., Cherry Hill, N.J., a regional banking
company, agreed to acquire J.A. Montgomery Inc., Wilmington, Del.,
an insurance brokerage firm. The financial terms of the deal were
not disclosed.
</P>
