</P>
<P>
   If the car is as advanced as the method being used to
manufacture it, then Skoda has reason to be quietly confident.
</P>
<P>
   Michael, one of 3,000 ``guest'' workers at the plant, is paid
16,000 crowns a month for working an eight-hour shift with a
